    <header>
        <h1><span class="title" itemprop="name" data-bind="text:title">How to Get Involved</span></h1>
    </header>

    <div class="bodysection">
        <div class="articleBody" itemprop="articleBody" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body"><h1><span>The Star and Shadow Cinema runs on the
love and work of a large and ever-growing collective of volunteers.</span></h1>
<p><b><span>Please help with Warwick Street
Refurbishment</span></b></p>
<p><span>The building we have purchased needs
full refurbishment. As much as possible will be done by volunteer labour.  Whatever your
skill-level you are welcome to come along and involved in the radical
refurbishment of our new home.</span></p>
<p><span>Turn up on site on the days mentioned
below and a site safety supervisor will give you an induction. </span></p>
<p><span>We've got protective clothing galore,
refreshments by the gallon and a massive skip that needs filling.</span></p>
<p><span>If you'd rather support us in other ways
we need a vegetarian communal meal cooked every Saturday. Or bake us a cake !!
 </span></p>
<p><span>To keep up to date with volunteering
opportunities make sure you sign up to </span><a href="http://www.starandshadow.org.uk/signup"><span>http://www.starandshadow.org.uk/signup</span></a></p>
<p><b><span>Opening times for
Refurbishment Volunteering:</span></b></p><ul><li><p><b>Monday to Friday 10am to 6pm SKILLED &amp; EXPERIENCED CONSTRUCTION VOLUNTEERS ONLY</b></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><b>Saturday &amp; Sunday 11am to 5</b><b>pm EVERYONE WELCOME</b></p></li></ul><ul>
</ul>
<p><span>We'd love to see you on these
volunteer days - no need to bring anything but your energy and enthusiasm!</span></p><p><span><strong></strong></span></p><p><b>Please help with Administration</b></p><p><span>We need volunteers to help in the Finance &amp; Admin Collective. Email us to find out how you can help.</span></p>
<h2> </h2>
<p><b><span>Future Needs</span></b></p>
<p><b><span>We expect to open
early 2018. </span></b><b><span>When we open we
will need volunteer workers in the following areas.</span></b></p>
<p><strong><span>film projection : bar work
: designing brochures and posters: database update : website update : emailing
: ushering : choosing films : planning festivals : booking bands: researching
new event ideas:: decorating : cleaning (those big windows won’t clean
themselves): tidying inside and outside: gardening: fixing broken things :
recycling : collecting freecycled things : sweeping : stocktaking : ordering
stock : writing copy : selling tickets : writing funding applications and
fundraising: bookkeeping : paying bills: 
managing our license : DJing : organising gigs : everything else and
more…</span></strong><strong></strong></p>
<p><span>You can volunteer for a job, a one-off
occasion, a regular weekly slot – however it best fits with you.</span></p>
<p></p>
<p><b><span>Put
on your own event at the Star &amp; Shadow</span></b></p>
<p><span>We run a unique
system of open programming whereby grass roots community organisations,
independent artists and any member of the public can come and promote their own
social causes via film, music, discussions and working groups. We provide the
space and facilities for this to happen. We will be open for events in June 2017. If you want to plan ahead contact details are below</span></p><p></p>
<h4></h4>
<p><b></b></p>
<p><b><span>Contact</span></b></p>
<ul>
<li><span>email: </span><span><a href="mailto:info@starandshadow.org.uk"><span>info@starandshadow.org.uk</span></a></span></li>
<li><span>Facebook: </span><span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/StarAndShadowCinema"><span>https://www.facebook.com/StarAndShadowCinema</span></a></span></li>
<li><span>Twitter: </span><span><a href="https://twitter.com/StarAndShadow"><span>@StarAndShadow</span></a></span></li>
<li><span>Get update emails: </span><span><a href="http://www.starandshadow.org.uk/signup"><span>http://www.starandshadow.org.uk/signup</span></a></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
</ul></div>
